703003f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ashland Place - Lafayette Avenue
703003f-a.text:
Ashland Place, at the northwest corner of Lafayette Avenue, showing
the Hotel Granda. The view is west from 'ulton treet.
P. L. perr  August 20, 1941
NO REPRODUCTIONS
